    {
        "content": "<p>Hi <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"1006888\">@Lukas Juhrich</span>,<br>\nBased on a quick check <code>parseAndCanonicalizeProgramPublishedRootsWithBuiltin</code> returns <code>ParsedResources</code> which contains a fully type checked <code>*ModuleEnv</code>. You should be able to render those types using <code>TypeWriter</code>.</p>",
        "id": 604124771,
        "sender_full_name": "Anton",
